title: Nyuzen Student Delegation to Visit Forest Grove (City of Forest Grove, OR)
text: ( Source : City of Forest Grove, OR ) Details Category : Latest News Mayor Peter Truax plans to formally welcome the student delegation upon their arrival on Thursday, October 29 , 2015 , 5:00 pm, in the Community Auditorium , 1915 Main Street .
